    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.35-36_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">35</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>Sunday, April 20</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt,</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I wanted to write you a note to tell you how very sorry I was to learn of yours wife's sudden passing. If anyone has ever prepared himself for such an event, I know that you have, for you hold
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.35-36_0002"/>
                    
                    such a beautiful concept of life now and in the future.</p>
                
                <p>Your way of living is a beautiful thing to watch, Dr. Neihardt. It is worth more than I can tell you to know you and to learn from you.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>With deepest sincerity,</salute>
                    
                    <signed>Mary Ann Shaw</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <note type="curatorial"><hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT CENTER</hi></note>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.35-36_0003"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">36</fw>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    COLUMBIA. MO.
                    APR21
                    8-AM
                    1958
                
                    PRAY
                    FOR
                    PEACE
                </ab>
                <figure>
                    <figDesc>3 Cent Stamp</figDesc>
                    <p>U.S. POSTAGE 3Â¢
                    IN GOD WE TRUST
                    LIBERTY</p>
                </figure>
                
                <ab type="address">
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt</addrLine>
                            <addrLine><hi rend="caps">R<unclear>F</unclear>D</hi> 7</addrLine>
